      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanical masterclass, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN ViscoLok limited-slip differential. The vehicle features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and is structurally immaculate, with the carbon fiber roof and subframe showing no signs of fatigue. Maintenance is current, including preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
