      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the wide-body, naturally aspirated 911. Powered by the M96/03 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, the powerplant delivers linear torque and a visceral soundtrack through the factory-tuned exhaust. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, utilizing its viscous multi-plate clutch all-wheel-drive system for surgical power distribution. This specimen features a pristine undercarriage, documented IMS/RMS service, and original paint with consistent depth. The braking system\u2014comprising four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors\u2014exhibits zero fade and immediate bite. A turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
